Secret Society Records, later renamed 
<a href="http://www.chungkingstudios.com/" target="_blank" title="Home">
<b>Chung King Studios</b></a>--a pun on 
owner John King's name. It's been called 
the Abbey Road of rap; Run-DMC, LL 
Cool J and The Beastie Boys 
all recorded their early hits here. 
Since relocated to <a href="7av.htm">Varick Street</a>.

